4 different pets are kept: cat, lizard, mouse, rabbit
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, snowmobile, train, trike
 1. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 2. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person traveling to edinburgh##3
 4. the owner of the rabbit is on the far right##1
 5. the person driving the trike is between the person traveling to london and the person traveling to new-york##2
 6. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
 8. the owner of the rabbit is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 9. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
10. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the lizard is the person traveling to london##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage    | soy-milk   | coffee | almond-milk | fanta      |
| City        | london | edinburgh | new-york   | hannover     |
| Pet         | lizard     | cat    | mouse       | rabbit     |
| Transport   | scooter    | trike  | train       | snowmobile |

