5. the person watching spy movies is between the chef and the person who growstulip##2
6. the journalist is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
7. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3
8. the chef is between the person watching comedy movies and the person who growsiris##2
9. the person eating banana is on the left of the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
