 8. the owner of the fish is on the right of the teacher##1
 9. the writer is on the left or right of the colombian##3
10. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the chinese##1
11. the colombian is on the left or right of the writer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |      3       |       4       |
| Nationality   | argentine    | dutch  | colombian       | chinese  |
| Job     | teacher    | designer | videographer | writer        |
| Pet     | pony       | fish     | dog          | chinchilla    |
